#. <section class="sutta" id="sn4.5"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn4.5:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn4.5:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. Life Span"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 5. Dutiyamārapāsasutta → dutiyapāsasuttaṃ (bj, s1-3) | pāsa (2) (pts1)
msgctxt "sn4.5:0.3"
msgid "5. Dutiyamārapāsasutta"
msgstr "5. Māra’s Snares (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.5:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā bārāṇasiyaṃ viharati isipatane migadāye."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Benares, in the deer park at "
"Isipatana."

msgctxt "sn4.5:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn4.5:1.3"
msgid "“bhikkhavo”ti."
msgstr "“Mendicants!”"

msgctxt "sn4.5:1.4"
msgid "“Bhadante”ti te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Venerable sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "sn4.5:1.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.106"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.237"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.5:2.1"
msgid "“Muttāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sabbapāsehi ye dibbā ye ca mānusā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, I am freed from all snares, both human and divine."

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.2"
msgid "Tumhepi, bhikkhave, muttā sabbapāsehi ye dibbā ye ca mānusā."
msgstr "You are also freed from all snares, both human and divine."

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.3"
msgid ""
"Caratha, bhikkhave, cārikaṃ bahujanahitāya bahujanasukhāya lokānukampāya "
"atthāya hitāya sukhāya devamanussānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Wander forth, mendicants, for the welfare and happiness of the people, out "
"of compassion for the world, for the benefit, welfare, and happiness of gods "
"and humans."

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.4"
msgid "Mā ekena dve agamittha."
msgstr "Let not two go by one road."

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.5"
msgid ""
"Desetha, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ "
"sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāsetha."
msgstr ""
"Teach the Dhamma that’s good in the beginning, good in the middle, and good "
"in the end, meaningful and well-phrased. And reveal a spiritual practice "
"that’s entirely full and pure."

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.6"
msgid "Santi sattā apparajakkhajātikā, assavanatā dhammassa parihāyanti."
msgstr ""
"There are beings with little dust in their eyes. They’re in decline because "
"they haven’t heard the teaching."

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.7"
msgid "Bhavissanti dhammassa aññātāro."
msgstr "There will be those who understand the teaching!"

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.8"
msgid ""
"Ahampi, bhikkhave, yena uruvelā senānigamo tenupasaṅkamissāmi "
"dhammadesanāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"I will travel to Uruvelā, the village of Senāni, in order to teach the "
"Dhamma.”"

msgctxt "sn4.5:2.9"
msgid ""
"Atha kho māro pāpimā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "Then Māra the Wicked went up to the Buddha and addressed him in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.5:3.1"
msgid "“Baddhosi sabbapāsehi,"
msgstr "“You’re bound by all snares,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:3.2"
msgid "ye dibbā ye ca mānusā;"
msgstr "both human and divine."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:3.3"
msgid "Mahābandhanabaddhosi,"
msgstr "You’re bound by the great bond:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:3.4"
msgid "na me samaṇa mokkhasī”ti."
msgstr "you won’t escape me, ascetic!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.5:4.1"
msgid "“Muttāhaṃ sabbapāsehi,"
msgstr "“I’m freed from all snares,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:4.2"
msgid "Ye dibbā ye ca mānusā;"
msgstr "both human and divine."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:4.3"
msgid "Mahābandhanamuttomhi,"
msgstr "I’m freed from the great bonds;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn4.5:4.4"
msgid "Nihato tvamasi antakā”ti."
msgstr "You’re beaten, terminator!”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn4.5:5.1"
msgid "Atha kho māro pāpimā … pe … tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr "Then Māra … vanished right there."
